OL,5, The treatment of whistleblowers at the 
OL,6, United Nations should be examined by an
OL,7, external panel, its former spokeswoman 
OL,8, on sexual harassment has said.         
OL,10,FPurna Sen's comments follow a BBC      
OL,11,Finvestigation which revealed the       
OL,12,Fsackings of a number of UN staff who   
OL,13,Ftried to expose alleged wrongdoing.    
OL,15,FMs Sen said the UN should "step up" and
OL,16,Fadopt any suggestions made by a panel. 
OL,18,FThe UN has said it is committed to     
OL,19,Fprotecting "bona fide whistleblowers"  
OL,20,Fand holding staff accountable.         
